    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Arm Strike against Parry\nType: Normal\nQi: 12\n\nWith a mere touch you can destroy most demons, causing them to disappear in a flash of dust and heat. Make an Arm Strike against the Parry of any Demon. If you succeed the creature is completely destroyed. It does not work if the Demon has Qi rank and they exceed your own. This works against standard demons and against Qi Spirits. However against Ogre Demons, it does not destroy them automatically, rather you roll 6d10 Open Damage against them plus do 6 Extra Wounds.",
